tokens.css — Full design token system extending the existing palette:

Colors: preserve ink/paper/terra/olive/slate/plum/amber + add functional mappings
Typography: fluid clamp() scale, Fraunces optical size settings for display/heading/body
Spacing: 8pt grid system
Layout: content width 42rem, page width 72rem
Borders, shadows, transitions, z-index layers
Column-specific full color mappings (not just dots — full page tinting)

